UN Defuses Dispute Between European Union, India at Global Warming Meeting

-- B y   E w a   K r u k o w s k a
-- 
2011-12-11T01:37:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-11/un-defuses-dispute-between-eu-india-global-warming-talks-to-continue.html
European Union Climate Commissioner
 Connie Hedegaard  said she’d accept language in a pact being
drawn up at United Nations global warming talks calling for an
outcome with “legal force” limiting fossil fuels.  Hedegaard and  India ’s environment minister said they agreed
the new language to allow UN climate talks to advance today in
Durban,  South Africa .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ewa Krukowska in Brussels at 
 ekrukowska@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
